  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You've had enough! Peter and the other kids are manipulative little goblins, and for some reason, the teacher is trying to catch YOU! This terror will <i>never</i> stop. There is only one solution. You have to escape. For good. Escape before your parents come to pick you up. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>no the baby </strong>is a stealth-horror game about a child trying to escape a strange kindergarten filled with puzzles, oddities and annoying children.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266620/extras/d74c33507c209abc43118380559979c9.avif?t=1743776430\" width=208 height=158 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore kindergarten</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find items</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run from teacher</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hate the Peter</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sneak around</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features some tunes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crisp textures</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Evil contraptions</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266620/extras/d1139cafa6a08f9a206c1f0f6867af1f.avif?t=1743776430\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266620/extras_big/d1139cafa6a08f9a206c1f0f6867af1f.avif?t=1743776430 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"no, the baby. no the baby. no the, baby. no. the baby\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
